data.description: Check out this hard to find Rancher in Hampton.  Located minutes for Peninsula Town Center and the interstate.  Roof installed Jan 24, brand new carpet, new cabinets and granite counter tops, freshly painted and new floor coverings in kitchen & bath.  Enjoy the screened in back porch plus fenced backyard. You will like the large living room with cathedral ceiling that open up to kitchen.  Some repairs still to be done.  See other items listed on sheet in listing or call LA.
